data.description: OPEN HOUSE, SUNDAY, AUGUST 27th 2-4 PM... Welcome home to this charmer in the quiet subdivision of Oakwood Manor. This home features a spacious 1.15 acre lot giving some privacy between you and your neighbors. Great layout with separate dining room between kitchen and den.  The master suite has an en-suite bathroom that features separate shower, jetted tub, and double vanity. Conveniently located near Chatsworth and Dalton and only 10 minutes to mall. We will be LIVE for showings on THURSDAY, August 17th, 2023.
